Senior Official Meets Brazilian Foreign Minister
BEIJING , November 30 ( Xinhua ) -- Senior official Liu Jibin said here today that China attaches great importance on cooperation with Brazil in the space sector .
Liu Jibin , minister of China 's Commission of Science , Technology and Industry for National Defense , made the remark in a meeting with Brazilian Foreign Minister Luiz Felipe Lampreia .
He pointed to the good bilateral relations , and said China hopes that cooperation between the two nations in the space sector will serve as a good example for developing countries .
Liu expressed his belief that international cooperation will become the trend for providing space-related services to countries throughout the world .
He briefed Lampreia on the development of China 's space technology and the nation 's international cooperation in using space science for peaceful purpose .
Lampreia said Brazil is fully prepared to establish medium - and long-term cooperation with China in the realm of space exploration .
